So I’ll work on it.

00:02:30.750 --> 00:02:32.460
I’m excited for this series.

00:02:32.460 --> 00:02:33.780
Some of these things I’ve thought about.

00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:35.860
Some, I’ll be learning along with you.

00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:36.860
It’s gonna be fun.

00:02:36.860 --> 00:02:39.690
Cause at the end of the day statistics are
about us.

00:02:39.690 --> 00:02:40.460
People.

00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:41.480
And our world.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:42.640
And how we relate to each other.

